<http://www.spektrix.com/factorytheatre/event/144603ADGKPRRVBNNLQRQJGLGLVRLKGRL> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Kitchen Potluck 2026";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Welcome to the Kitchen!</span></span><span><br/></span>fu-GEN's longstanding annual tradition of Kitchen Potluck returns this season with three incredible writers, three phenomenal dramaturges, and a troupe of formidable actors to bring everything to life! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Potluck began before fu-GEN was a company in 2002-a small group of Asian Canadian artists would bring food, gather, and read new works they were writing and look for feedback and encouragement. This tradition has grown into the incredible community you see today, encompassing hundreds of audience members, and supporting hundreds of artists. Celebrating the Asian Canadian new play tradition while closing out another fu-GEN season, we hope you can join us for an evening of joyous camaraderie, delicious food, and a wonderful party.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Playwrights:</span></span><span><br/></span>Lucy Coren, Ho Ka Kei (Jeff Ho), Irene (Fan) Yi<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Dramaturges:</span></span><span><br/></span>Crystal Lee, Tawiah M'Carthy, Marie Beath Badian<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Cast:</span></span><span><br/></span>Jeff Yung, Lindsay Wu, Jobina Sitoh, Madelaine Hodges, Jeff Ho<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Your Co-Hosts:</span></span><span><br/></span>Nina Lee Aquino, 郝邦宇 Steven Hao<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">fu-GEN Team:</span></span><span><br/></span>Artistic Director: David Yee<span><br/></span>Managing Producer: Marissa Orjalo<span><br/></span>Resident Dramaturge: Andy Cheng<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Thank you to fu-GEN's generous donors for their constant support:<span><br/></span>TD Ready Commitment, The Wuchien Michael Than Foundation, Canada Council for the Arts, Ontario Arts Council, Toronto Arts Council. Our programming is made possible through your belief in our mission.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Duration: 75 mins<span><br/></span>Age Recommendation: 15+
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-06-15T20:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/factorytheatre/files/558dcdb1-abef-460b-a501-83640495bf05.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/factorytheatre/location/1AHGJDSMMPLMPPGNLJBQVLBRSKVDLQRPP>;
  schema:offers _:c5a4b28f60d54d888edb71ae5e343b02280;
  schema:duration "PT75M";
  schema:endDate "2026-06-15T21:15:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

