<http://www.spektrix.com/factorytheatre/event/144402ACVKCPVTMPTSGMJVJCRGKDDCBSG> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Thrustfest | July 24";
  schema:description """
	THRUST FEST is a brand new drag festival highlighting the brilliance, elegance, talent, and star power of Drag Kings! The show festival nights will be held July 24-26, 2026 at Factory Theatre. Three nights of shows, two days of workshops, one drag king festival! International team Riley Poppyseed, Kreme Inakuchi, and Throb Zombie have banded together to bring you an incredible summer weekend full of showcases, competition, education, and TALENT!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Tipping is highly encouraged! Bring cash to tip your performers!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Consent is mandatory and goes both ways- you don't touch performers and they don't touch you without enthusiastic consent. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Masking is HIGHLY encouraged! Please protect our community and performers by wearing a mask when not eating or drinking. Masks will be available at the door, and HEPA filters will be running.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>First come, first served for seating. NO BALCONY SEATING: reserved for performers.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Duration: 150 minutes<span><br/></span>Age Recommendation: 18+<span><br/></span>Content & Sensory Warnings: flashing lights / very loud noises / haze / mature content / adult themes / partial nudity<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>HEADLINERS:<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>HercuSleaze<span><br/></span>Jarvis Hammer<span><br/></span>Yuen Young<span><br/></span>Riley Poppyseed<span><br/></span>Kreme Inakuchi<span><br/></span>Throb Zombie<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>HOSTS:<span><br/></span>Jarvis Hammer<span><br/></span>Throb Zombie<span><br/></span>Pressure K<span><br/></span>SHERMAN<span><br/></span>Ivory<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>PERFORMERS | NIGHT ONE (July 24):<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Holiday Kings<span><br/></span>Luciano VeriNotti<span><br/></span>Shayne Nash<span><br/></span>Freddy Prinze Charming<span><br/></span>Angus Beef<span><br/></span>Connor Ria!<span><br/></span>King Freddie<span><br/></span>Sir Maxim<span><br/></span>Danny Fox-Trot & Logan Liqueur<span><br/></span>Precious Julz<span><br/></span>Chey Boi<span><br/></span>Cyrus K. Stratton<span><br/></span>Pølterguy<span><br/></span>Harley Sayne<span><br/></span>Spank Knightly<span><br/></span>Tuna Melt<span><br/></span>Benedick the Bastard<span><br/></span>DeVery Bess<span><br/></span>Maximum Capacity<span><br/></span>Cyril Cinder
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-07-24T20:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
